% Bar 2: F major
% S1: c/ A2 F/
% S2: A/ F2 C/  (third below)
% A1: F/ C2 A/  (arpeggiate down chord tones)
% A2: F/ F2 F/  (original alto, oblique)
% T1 (written): C/ A2 F/  concert: C4 A3 F3
% T2 (written): A,/ F2 C/ concert: A2 F2? — F2 is below T2 comfortable range. Use C/ A2 F/ wait, T2 min G2.
%   T2 written A,/ = concert A2 ok. F2? — too low for T2. Use C/ instead: C/ A,2 C/  concert C3 A2 C3 — ok
% Bar: F, F,/ F, A,,/ concert F2 — ok
% B1: F,/ F,2 A,,/  concert F2 then A1 — ok
[V:1] c/ A2 F/ |
[V:2] A/ F2 C/ |
[V:3] F/ C2 A/ |
[V:4] F/ F2 F/ |
[V:5] C/ A2 F/ |
[V:6] C/ A,2 C/ |
[V:7] F, F,/ F, A,,/ |
[V:8] F,/ F,2 A,,/ |
